## Stack

- **Frontend:** React 19, Zustand, Tailwind CSS v4, Vite
- **Backend:** FastAPI, Pydantic, uvicorn
- **Tooling:** pnpm, Turborepo, Biome, Ruff, Docker, husky, commitlint

## Getting started

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# Start development (frontend + backend)
pnpm dev
```

- Frontend: http://localhost:5173
- Backend: http://localhost:8000
- API docs: http://localhost:8000/docs

## Project structure

```
packages/
├── frontend/   # React 19 + Vite + Tailwind + Zustand
├── shared/     # Shared TypeScript types and utilities
└── backend/    # FastAPI + Pydantic (runs in Docker)
```

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pnpm dev` | Start frontend + backend in development mode |
| `pnpm build` | Build all TypeScript packages |
| `pnpm typecheck` | Type-check all TypeScript packages |
| `pnpm check` | Run Biome linter/formatter |
| `pnpm verify` | Run all checks (TypeScript + Python) |

## Conventions

- **Commits:** [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) enforced via commitlint
- **Scopes:** `frontend`, `shared`, `backend`, `deps`, `docker`
- **Formatting:** Biome (TypeScript), Ruff (Python) — both run on pre-commit
